						"title": "Speed time-to-value for your app modernization strategy",
						"subtitle": " Best practices to accelerate your cloud-native app modernization",
						"copy": "Successful app modernization requires balancing investments, benefits, and business constraints. Cloud-native infrastructure and technology play a key role in accelerating this process, and enabling workload decentralization and platform-driven innovation. While transforming complex applications can introduce new challenges, modernization is essential for adopting a modern cloud strategy and unlocking advanced capabilities such as AI/ML. \n\nThe Forrester __best practices: Cloud-Native app modernization__ report defines the three key goals of modernization, five major modernization approaches, and five constraints that organizations need to navigate.\n\n<img src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/1srbLIdvjEGhX139cNxhXw/23ac683623866fe28e38f3554939b18d/Forrester_TL.png\" alt=\"Forrester thought leadership cover\"/>",
